-Be gentle. You can't do it like this.
-Madam Zhang!

16
00:02:39,690 --> 00:02:42,190
-Keep an eye on them.
-Be careful.

17
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:49,079
What happened? Why are you in such a rush?

18
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:52,040
Wei Ying Ning is my sister.

19
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:58,000
Come with me.

20
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:03,360
I told you many times
not to mention this name again.

21
