25
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,930
-But so what?
-Why?

26
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:19,150
What do you mean by why?

27
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:28,420
I told you not to mention her because
I was very disappointed in her.

28
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:31,740
Your older sister committed
a grave mistake.

29
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:35,120
Everyone is saying that
my sister committed a mistake.

30
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:38,030
What mistake did she commit?

31
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:44,670
Madam, say something.

32
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:48,940
Why is everyone so
tight-lipped with this question?

33
00:03:50,490 --> 00:03:55,350
I racked my brain to get into this
Forbidden City just to find out the truth.

34
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:59,579
Madam, please tell me the truth.

35
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:09,720
Man did a scandalous act
and was found out by others.

36
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:12,230
What scandalous act?

37
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:17,630
For a woman, what else
is more important than her chastity?

38
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:22,070
One night, she didn't return
the whole night.

39
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:26,600
When she returned the next morning,
she got caught by Chief Wu.

40
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:33,320
They even found her soiled inner skirt
near the Imperial Garden's fake mountain.

41
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,990
My sister had always led
a clean and honest life.

42
00:04:35,990 --> 00:04:39,530
-She would not do such a thing.
-I also didn't believe it.

43
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:43,909
Man is a very gentle and kind lady.

44
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,600
She would not have an illicit affair.

45
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,940
But I had personally asked her.

46
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:54,670
No matter how I asked her,
she gave me only one answer.

47
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:58,290
She said that no one forced her
and that it was with her consent.

48
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:02,640
According to the palace rules,
she should be caned to death.

49
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:06,910
That time, Empress Dowager was ill.

50
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:09,190
Any bloodshed was forbidden in the palace.

51
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:14,790
Hence, she was caned 50 times
and was expelled.

52
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:23,190
I never thought that your sister would
commit suicide because of it.

53
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:25,360
Everyone said that my sister...

54
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:29,460
hung herself out of shame.

55
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:34,190
But I checked her wound. She has bruises
in the shape of fingers on her neck.

56
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,520
My sister was strangled to death.

57
00:05:36,690 --> 00:05:38,460
