extremely wasteful.

234
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:21,380
They always make it into a competition
and if this continues,

235
00:20:22,290 --> 00:20:26,610
it'll create an unhealthy atmosphere
within the harem.

236
00:20:28,390 --> 00:20:30,590
What is your suggestion then?

237
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:34,800
As the empress, I need to lead by example.

238
00:20:34,980 --> 00:20:39,070
First, I'll abandon
the pearl and jade ornaments...

239
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:43,400
